Krueger, B. J., Grassian, V. H., Laskin, A. and Cowin, J. P., “The Transformation of Solid Atmospheric Particles into Liquid Droplets through Heterogeneous Chemistry: Laboratory Insights into the Processing of Calcium Containing Mineral Dust Aerosol in the Troposphere” Geophys. Res. Letts. 2003 30, 48-1 to 48-4. (DOI 10.1029/2002GL016563)